imdb.plot outline: Ever wondered where your donations go? Journey with Developing Destinations each week, as we venture into unknown territory, exploring worlds living below the line. We step outside the realms of normal travel shows as we take you on a ride into the lives of the few. Delivering stories of hope, dreams and adventure from around the globe. See life from a different perspective as we follow Sean Cassar, creator and host of DD, as he interviews a vast array of people varying from locals and human rights activists, to military and politicians in locations where nobody else dares to go. Painting an accurate picture of resilience, strength, dreams and hope. All while discovering the beauty of these developing destinations.
